ue for deriving girls' names from vocabulary words denoting flowers.  See also  Daisy ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Marguerite de Ferrers was born in 1236, in Derbyshire, England, United Kingdom. She married Robert de Neufbourg about 1253. They were the parents of at least 2 daughters. She died on 20 May 1287, in Blainville, Seine-Maritime, Normandy, France, at the age of 51."},"et":{"1236–20 May 1287":"1236–20. mai 1287","1225–1296":"1225–1296","1250–1290":"1250–1290","1253–Female":"1253–Surnud","1236–1287":"1236–1287","1236":"1236","1225":"1225","20 May 1287":"20. mai 1287","Abt 1253":"umbes 1253","1287":"1287","1253":"1253","1296":"1296","1250":"1250","1290":"1290","Ferrers, Derbyshire, England, United Kingdom":"Derbyshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Neufbourg, Seine-Maritime, Normandy, France":"Neufbourg, Seine-Maritime, Normandie, Prantsusmaa","Blainville, Seine-Maritime, Normandy, France":"Blainville, Seine-Maritime, Normandie, Prantsusmaa","France":"Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"1236–20 May 1287":"1236–20. toukokuuta 1287","1225–1296":"1225–1296","1250–1290":"1250–1290","1253–Female":"1253–Kuollut","1236–1287":"1236–1287","1236":"1236","1225":"1225","20 May 1287":"20. toukokuuta 1287","Abt 1253":"noin 1253","1287":"1287","1253":"1253","1296":"1296","1250":"1250","1290":"1290","Ferrers, Derbyshire, England, United Kingdom":"Derbyshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Neufbourg, Seine-Maritime, Normandy, France":"Neufbourg, Seine-Maritime, Normandie, Ranska","Blainville, Seine-Maritime, Normandy, France":"Blainville, Seine-Maritime, Normandie, Ranska","France":"Ranska"},"fr":{"1236–20 May 1287":"1236–20 mai 1287","1225–1296":"1225–1296","1250–1290":"1250–1290","1253–Female":"1253–Décédée","1236–1287":"1236–1287","1236":"1236","1225":"1225","20 May 1287":"20 mai 1287","Abt 1253":"environ 1253","1287":"1287","1253":"1253","1296":"1296","1250":"1250","1290":"1290","Ferrers, Derbyshire, England, United Kingdom":"Derbyshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Neufbourg, Se